      <h2 class="detail-page__heading">
        Seminar Information
      </h2>

      <p class="detail-page__lead">
        Seminars are available for groups of five or more participants.
        We offer programs such as Healthy Karate Seminars, Women's Self-Defense Seminars,
        and seminars for companies, schools, and other organizations.<br>
        These seminars are also suitable as part of employee orientation and mental resilience training.
        Experience seminars for international visitors are also available.<br>
        For more information, please <a href="#contact">contact us by email</a>.
      </p>

